-- Kobe Bryant Signs Two-Year Contract Extension With NBA’s Lakers
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2013-11-25T16:50:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-25/kobe-bryant-signs-two-year-contract-extension-with-nba-s-lakers.html
The Los Angeles Lakers signed Kobe
Bryant to a two-year contract extension, the National Basketball
Association team said in a statement.  Bryant, a 15-time All-Star who has helped the Lakers win
five NBA titles, hasn’t played since rupturing his left Achilles
tendon in April.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  